return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613620\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hxr1665702704973.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hxr1665702704973.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hxr1665702704973.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hxr1665702704973\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Using a U_VERSION Field in a Server Page\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Data integrity can be maintained using the U_VERSION field in a web application. You can copy the U_VERSION field to a hidden non-database field that is sent to the browser. When handling a request, compare the hidden field with the U_VERSION to decide if the modified data can be written to the database.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__context_w2706ab1b5b1_w2707ab1b5_w2708ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__topic_d22622e1_d22623e1_d22624e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__p_d22625e1_d22626e1_d22627e1\">The following is an example of using U_VERSION to\n               maintain the integrity of entity TIMESHEET.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11081e1_d11082e1_d11083e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the entity TIMESHEET, define a database field U_VERSION whose data type is\n               String with packing code C1. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11084e1_d11085e1_d11086e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the entity TIMESHEET, define non-database field DUMMY whose data type is String\n               with packing code C1 and with syntax HID. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11087e1_d11088e1_d11089e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Define a server page TEST_UVERSION. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11090e1_d11091e1_d11092e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Load fields of TIMESHEET in TEST_UVERSION except the U_VERSION field. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11093e1_d11094e1_d11095e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In TEST_UVERSION, add a button (SAVE) for submitting a request from a browser to\n               the server for saving the modified occurrences. </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11096e1_d11097e1_d11098e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Define an operation: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation carry_on\n webget\n webgen\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11099e1_d11100e1_d11101e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__p_d22628e1_d22629e1_d22630e1\">Set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Activation URL</span>\n               property of TIMESHEET as: TIMESHEET.carry_on. Waiting for developers. Activation URL\n               property may not be in v9.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11102e1_d11103e1_d11104e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Define an function: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">function save_u_version\n clear/e \"TIMESHEET\"\n retrieve/e \"TIMESHEET\"\n $1=1\n while($1-1 &lt; $hits(\"TIMESHEET\")) \n setocc \"TIMESHET\", \n $1 DUMMY=U_VERSION \n $1 = $1+1\n endwhile\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11105e1_d11106e1_d11107e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the exec operation of TIMESHEET, add: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">call save_u_version\nwebgen</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11108e1_d11109e1_d11110e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the Details trigger of button SAVE, add: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">store/e \"TIMESHEET\"\ncall save_u_version</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"hxr1665702704973__li_d11111e1_d11112e1_d11113e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the write trigger of entity TIMESHEET, add: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if (DUMMY = U_VERSION) \n write\nendif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwe1665702704830.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>U_VERSION for Improving Locking Performance</a><p>Uniface supports a version mechanism which can improve performance by using a field called U_VERSION. U_VERSION is a one-byte field which you must assign to an entity for it to work. In other words, it is not automatically available.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613620\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613620\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Using a U_VERSION Field in a Server Page Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Using a U_VERSION Field in a Server Page Data integrity can be maintained using the U_VERSION field in a web application. You can copy the U_VERSION field to a hidden non-database field that is sent to the browser. When handling a request, compare the hidden field with the U_VERSION to decide if the modified data can be written to the database. The following is an example of using U_VERSION to maintain the integrity of entity TIMESHEET. In the entity TIMESHEET, define a database field U_VERSION whose data type is String with packing code C1. In the entity TIMESHEET, define non-database field DUMMY whose data type is String with packing code C1 and with syntax HID. Define a server page TEST_UVERSION. Load fields of TIMESHEET in TEST_UVERSION except the U_VERSION field. In TEST_UVERSION, add a button (SAVE) for submitting a request from a browser to the server for saving the modified occurrences. Define an operation: operation carry_on webget webgen end Copy Set the Activation URL property of TIMESHEET as: TIMESHEET.carry_on. Waiting for developers. Activation URL property may not be in v9. Define an function: function save_u_version clear/e \"TIMESHEET\" retrieve/e \"TIMESHEET\" $1=1 while($1-1 < $hits(\"TIMESHEET\")) setocc \"TIMESHET\", $1 DUMMY=U_VERSION $1 = $1+1 endwhile end Copy In the exec operation of TIMESHEET, add: call save_u_version webgen Copy In the Details trigger of button SAVE, add: store/e \"TIMESHEET\" call save_u_version Copy In the write trigger of entity TIMESHEET, add: if (DUMMY = U_VERSION) write endif Copy Related Links U_VERSION for Improving Locking Performance Uniface supports a version mechanism which can improve performance by using a field called U_VERSION. U_VERSION is a one-byte field which you must assign to an entity for it to work. In other words, it is not automatically available. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}